{"type": "article", "id": 3596, "title": "Paul Smith 日本圣诞假日系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-17T08:01:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004208NubJqX9aAWsKIM23.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t今年的圣诞季，Paul Smith 日本推出了圣诞假日特别系列，包括针织毛衣、羊毛围巾、皮手套、领带、钱包、钥匙扣、手表以及男女皆宜的一组珠宝首饰。此外，这一圣诞限定系列还包括一款带 「Paul Smith」 字样的耳机，定价 32400 日元。从 Paul Smith 日本对外公布的图片来看，这一系列的单品都配有纯色的包装纸与丝带，非常适合作为圣诞礼物。目前，该系列部分单品已经上线 <a href=\"http://www.paulsmith.co.jp/shop/men/accessories/accessories/products/2408468900PS3_____\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Smith 日本网上商店</a>，而整个系列产品将于本月 22 日在日本的Paul Smith 实体店进行售卖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042047kGytqH2uYrmCNxU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004204WMKDJxYtzprHPiu6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004205MhdFRQHmyVD5eTJS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042064Pd7ILFbQkf9SHzv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042062tYGTEiMkCaeuzyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042068BNs6G5QiqVdJhDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004207qLldiCR6sjbAMOpw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}